snippet.title: The Chant - Reel 2 - Search for Hannah
snippet.description:
In the second of #TheChant’s “Reels” series of videos we’re taking a deeper look into the story of Hannah, one of our fellow attendants at the Prismic Spiritual Retreat, through the eyes of her brother Thomas.
Will Hannah ever come back to her family after fighting her inner demons on Glory Island? 
Find out when The Chant launches on November 3rd, 2022 on PC, PS5 and Xbox Series consoles!

Pre-order your copy now at https://www.thechant.com and follow The Chant on social to keep up to date:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheChantGame
Facebook: https://facebook.com/TheChantGame
Instagram: https://instagram.com/thechantgame
Official Website: https://www.thechant.com

#TheChant #HorrorGame #PrimeMatter #horrorgaming
